wikipedia_page.main: Edgar Tinkler (11 March 1921 – 14 November 2011), known as Ted, is a former English first-class cricketer who played in three matches. His debut was for Worcestershire in 1953 and two more for Marylebone Cricket Club (MCC) in the early 1960s.
